/// NACA App Configuration — TEMPLATE.
///
/// `lib/config.dart` is gitignored and must NOT be committed. Two ways to create it:
///   • Local dev:  cp lib/config.dart.example lib/config.dart  then replace
///                 __NACA_AUTH_TOKEN__ with the real backend token.
///   • CI:         the deploy workflow generates lib/config.dart from this template,
///                 injecting __NACA_AUTH_TOKEN__ from the NACA_AUTH_TOKEN GitHub secret.
///
/// supabaseAnonKey + URLs are PUBLIC client values (the anon key is RLS-gated and is
/// designed to ship in the client) — they live here in the clear on purpose. The only
/// value kept out of the repo is the backend authToken.
